title: (Tues Full) Morgan Pays Her Punishment + Lunchbox Tries to Book Criminals Hotel Room + Never Gonna Get It: Americans eat 4 of these per week!
itunes:title: (Tues Full) Morgan Pays Her Punishment + Lunchbox Tries to Book Criminals Hotel Room + Never Gonna Get It: Americans eat 4 of these per week!
description:
Morgan pays up and has to hold a sign out on the street today after losing the US State Capital Games last week. Lunchbox tries to book a room at the hotel that the escape prisoner and guard stayed at last month. He reveals why he can’t share the audio but what details he learned. We play a round of Never Gonna Get It where the question is: Americans eat 4 of these per week!
